---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Full Camp Claude cohort"
  description="Five live sessions, eight weeks, real supervision of Claude doing your work. For Foundations graduates ready to go deeper."
  activeNav="cohort"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Full Camp Claude · Eight-week cohort</div>
      <h1>Five live sessions. Eight weeks. <em>Real supervision</em> of Claude doing your work.</h1>
      <p class="dek">For Foundations graduates and working professionals ready to go deeper — supervision, multi-step tasks, custom skills, and a capstone automation that's yours by week eight.</p>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>5 × 90 min live sessions</span><span class="dot">·</span>
        <span>10–14 learners per cohort</span><span class="dot">·</span>
        <span>Next cohort · Fall 2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="price-card">
      <div class="label">Full Camp Claude</div>
      <div class="prereq">Prereq · Foundations cohort or equivalent</div>
      <div class="amount"><span class="currency">$</span>999</div>
      <div class="amount-note">One-time · Eight-week program</div>
      <ul>
        <li>5 live 90-minute sessions</li>
        <li>Biweekly cadence — build between</li>
        <li>Private cohort community + 60-day Q&amp;A</li>
        <li>Real capstone automation you keep</li>
        <li>1:1 review of your first skill</li>
        <li>Foundations grads get $100 off</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="buy-btn" href="/cohort/full/enroll">Reserve a seat →</a>
      <div class="guarantee"><strong>Application-based.</strong> We match cohort composition carefully. 48-hour response.</div>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <section class="strip cream">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Is this the right cohort?</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">Two cohorts. One <em>progression</em>.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Foundations teaches the map. Full Camp Claude is where you live inside it long enough that the work starts to do itself.</p>

      <div class="compare">
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="label">Cohort one</div>
          <h3>Foundations</h3>
          <div class="price">$299</div>
          <ul>
            <li>4 × 60 min sessions over 4 weeks</li>
            <li>The three doors, the levers, the equation</li>
            <li>One simple automation by the end</li>
            <li>Best for: AI-fluent professionals new to Claude</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/cohort">See Foundations →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar featured">
          <div class="label">Cohort two · You are here</div>
          <h3>Full <em>Camp Claude</em></h3>
          <div class="price">$999</div>
          <ul>
            <li>5 × 90 min sessions over 8 weeks</li>
            <li>Supervision, multi-step tasks, custom skills</li>
            <li>Real capstone automation</li>
            <li>1:1 review of your first production skill</li>
            <li>Best for: Foundations grads, power users</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="strip">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">The five sessions</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">What you'll <em>actually do</em>.</h2>

      <div class="sessions">
        <div class="session">
          <div class="num">Session <span class="big">01</span></div>
          <div><h4>Recap &amp; chat fluency at depth</h4><span class="outcome">Outcome: Three live Projects with real ongoing work</span></div>
          <p>Fast recap of Foundations. Deep dive on Chat Projects, Artifacts, context mechanics. Model selection by task type.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="session">
          <div class="num">Session <span class="big">02</span></div>
          <div><h4>Connectors &amp; <em>skills</em> at depth</h4><span class="outcome">Outcome: Three connectors + two custom skills</span></div>
          <p>Install the connectors your workflow actually needs. Write your first real <code>CLAUDE.md</code> skills.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="session">
          <div class="num">Session <span class="big">03</span></div>
          <div><h4>Graduating to <em>Cowork</em></h4><span class="outcome">Outcome: Three Cowork Projects for real work</span></div>
          <p>The emotional shift from Chat to Cowork. The sandbox at depth. Real Projects with real stakes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="session">
          <div class="num">Session <span class="big">04</span></div>
          <div><h4>Supervision &amp; the <em>competency ladder</em></h4><span class="outcome">Outcome: You've caught and corrected a Claude mistake</span></div>
          <p>Trust the Boundary → Read the Work → Delegate with Checkpoints. Real multi-file task with review.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="session">
          <div class="num">Session <span class="big">05</span></div>
          <div><h4>Automation · The <em>capstone</em></h4><span class="outcome">Outcome: One live automation running</span></div>
          <p>Build a real scheduled automation. Leave with something running daily that produces output you'll use tomorrow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="strip ink">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="final-cta">
        <div class="section-eyebrow center">Fall 2026</div>
        <h2>Application-based.<br/>Cohort <em>size of ten</em>.</h2>
        <p>Peer composition is half the value. Tell us about your work and what you want Claude to do for you.</p>
        <a href="/cohort/full/enroll" class="big-btn">Apply — $999</a>
        <p class="tiny">Foundations grads · $100 off · applied at checkout</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 72px 48px 56px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 400px; gap: 72px; align-items: start; }
  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 72px; line-height: 0.98; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink); margin: 0 0 24px; text-wrap: balance; }
  h1 em { color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; }
  .dek { font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; font-size: 26px; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 32px; max-width: 48ch; }
  .meta { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .meta span { margin-right: 28px; }
  .meta .dot { color: var(--rust); margin: 0 12px; }

  .price-card { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); border-radius: 3px; padding: 36px 32px; position: sticky; top: 24px; }
  .price-card .label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust-soft); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .price-card .prereq { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--rust-soft); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244,238,227,0.12); }
  .price-card .amount { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 88px; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.03em; font-style: italic; }
  .price-card .amount .currency { font-size: 36px; vertical-align: super; color: var(--rust-soft); margin-right: 6px; }
  .price-card .amount-note { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(244,238,227,0.6); margin: 12px 0 28px; }
  .price-card ul { margin: 0 0 28px; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
  .price-card li { padding: 10px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; border-top: 1px solid rgba(244,238,227,0.12); display: flex; gap: 12px; }
  .price-card li::before { content: "+"; color: var(--rust-soft); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 14px; }
  .price-card .buy-btn { display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 2px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; }
  .price-card .buy-btn:hover { background: var(--rust-soft); color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; }
  .price-card .guarantee { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgba(244,238,227,0.72); margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(244,238,227,0.12); }

  .strip { padding: 80px 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .strip .inner { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .strip.cream { background: var(--cream); }
  .strip.ink { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); border-top: none; }
  .section-eyebrow { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .section-eyebrow.center { text-align: center; }
  .strip.ink .section-eyebrow { color: var(--rust-soft); }
  .section-h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 52px; line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 28px; text-wrap: balance; }
  .section-h2 em { color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; }
  .lead { max-width: 62ch; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 17px; }

  .compare { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .pillar { background: var(--paper); padding: 36px 32px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 3px; }
  .pillar.featured { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); border: none; }
  .pillar .label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .pillar.featured .label { color: var(--rust-soft); }
  .pillar h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .pillar h3 em { color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; }
  .pillar.featured h3 em { color: var(--rust-soft); }
  .pillar .price { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 44px; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-style: italic; margin: 8px 0 20px; }
  .pillar ul { padding: 0; margin: 0 0 20px; list-style: none; }
  .pillar li { padding: 10px 0; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft); display: flex; gap: 12px; }
  .pillar.featured li { border-top-color: rgba(244,238,227,0.12); }
  .pillar li::before { content: "+"; color: var(--sage); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 14px; }
  .pillar.featured li::before { color: var(--rust-soft); }
  .pillar a { color: var(--rust); }

  .sessions { margin-top: 40px; }
  .session { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr 2fr; gap: 48px; padding: 36px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); align-items: baseline; }
  .session:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .session .num { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); }
  .session .num .big { display: block; font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; font-size: 64px; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink); margin-top: 4px; text-transform: none; }
  .session h4 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .session h4 em { color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; }
  .session p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0; max-width: 54ch; }
  .session .outcome { display: block; margin-top: 12px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sage); }

  .final-cta { text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .final-cta h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; font-size: 64px; line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--paper); margin: 0 0 24px; font-style: italic; text-wrap: balance; }
  .final-cta h2 em { color: var(--rust-soft); font-style: italic; }
  .final-cta p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.55; color: rgba(244,238,227,0.72); margin: 0 0 36px; }
  .final-cta .big-btn { display: inline-block; background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); padding: 18px 32px; border-radius: 2px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
  .final-cta .big-btn:hover { background: var(--rust-soft); }
  .final-cta .tiny { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 13px; font-family: var(--mono); letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: rgba(244,238,227,0.4); }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding: 48px 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: 44px; }
    .price-card { position: static; }
    .compare { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .session { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .strip { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .section-h2 { font-size: 36px; }
    .final-cta h2 { font-size: 40px; }
  }
</style>
